Eaves Costume Co., Respondent, v. Pratt, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 9, 1892.) Action by the Eaves Costume Company against Thomas H. Pratt,

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bookstaver and Pryor, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs.
